### Get all catches
GET http://localhost:3000/catches HTTP/1.1



### Retrieve catch by CATCH_ID:
GET  http://localhost:3000/catches/{{CATCH_ID}} HTTP/1.1

### Retrieve catch for non-existent id:
GET  http://localhost:3000/catches/{{NON_EXISTENT_CATCH_ID}} HTTP/1.1

### Update by catch id
PUT http://localhost:3000/catches/{{CATCH_ID}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "date": "2026-07-06",
    "species": "brown trout",
    "weight": 3.2,
    "length_in": 14,
    "bait": "Nightcrawler",
    "story": "It was a miracle!",
    "location": {
        "type": "Point",
        "coordinates": [37.4525, 118.7372] 
    }
}

### Delete by catch id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/catches/{{CATCH_ID}} HTTP/1.1